<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Yelpcamp</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        background: url("https://source.unsplash.com/random/?camping")
          center/cover no-repeat;
        background-color: #000000;
        margin: 0;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
      }

      .yelpcamp-info {
        max-width: 400px;
        font-size: 1.4em !important;
        text-align: left;
        color: #ffffff;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin: 15px;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="yelpcamp-info">
      <h1>Welcome to Yelpcamp</h1>
      <p>
        Immerse yourself in the wonders of nature and plan your next adventure
        with Yelpcamp. Uncover extraordinary campgrounds, forge connections with
        fellow nature enthusiasts, and craft enduring memories that last a
        lifetime.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're a seasoned outdoor explorer or venturing into camping for
        the first time, Yelpcamp beckons with a diverse array of campgrounds
        tailored to your preferences. Begin your expedition today!
      </p>
      <div style="background-color: #8f7458">
        <center><a class="nav-link" href="/login">Let's Go....</a></center>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Yelpcamp. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS script -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
